      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Add the<strong> grated carrot</strong>, <strong>champagne lentils </strong>and <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>to the dish and cook for 30 secs</p>",
