    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>thyme </strong>(chuck it in, stalk and all!), <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>to the dish</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and the <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>",
