    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the<strong> shredded kale</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Stir in the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and add 600ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>to the dish</p><p>Stir through the <strong>macaroni </strong>and <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>kale</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
